# UI components: shadcn/ui

- **Default**: Use shadcn/ui components for all UI elements (prefer installing an existing shadcn component over building a bespoke one).
- **Initialization**: If shadcn/ui is not initialized in this repo, run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

- **Adding components**: If a needed component is not installed, add it via:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component>
```

Example:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```
